  "time_ut": 1662365554,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0ddd 02\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd6",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A woman was killed with 02 kilos of drug",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Anuradhapura headquarters police said that a woman was arrested today (5th) along with more than 2 kilos of heroin worth more than five crore rupees, which is the largest haul of heroin drugs ever seized by the Anuradhapura police.",
        "Police say that the person arrested was a 26-year-old Dravidian woman who was residing in a line room in Elugolla Watta area of \u200b\u200bRangala Police Domain, Kandy.",
        "According to a statement given by the suspect who was a resident of Kottawa area who was engaged in cloth trade near Anuradhapura Hospital, who was arrested yesterday (4th) at Bhatia Mawatha, Anuradhapura, with 630 grams of heroin, the police said that the suspect was arrested along with this heroin.",
        "According to the information of the suspect, a group of officers from the anti-corruption division of the Anuradhapura headquarters police went to the Rangala area of \u200b\u200bKandy and arrested the suspect along with two kilos and 10 grams of heroin, and it was revealed that she was the sister-in-law of the first suspect who was arrested yesterday (4th) in Anuradhapura. .",
        "Police say that the suspect's 28-year-old husband was also killed in a shooting by a group of drug dealers in Theldeniya area of \u200b\u200bKandy last April.",
        "The police say that the statements made by the suspect have been recorded that after the death of her husband, the first suspect, who is her brother-in-law, brought one kilo of this heroin drug stock, which was hidden in the line room, to Anuradhapura.",
        "The arrested suspect was to be produced before the Anuradhapura Magistrate Court."
      ],
